WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.167
I descend a staircase built from my own questions.

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:11.200
Inside each thought, another mirror waits, breathing softly.

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:17.700
The mind folds inward, a theater lit by electric dusk.

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:24.717
I vanish into the watcher watching the watcher.

